
# Commands to apply Bayesian neural network to a 3-way classification problem.

net-spec clog 4 8 3 / - x0.2:0.5:1 0.05:0.5 - x0.05:0.5 - 0.05:0.5 
model-spec clog class

data-spec clog 4 1 3 / cdata@1:400 . cdata@401:1000 .

net-gen clog fix 0.5
mc-spec clog repeat 10 sample-noise heatbath hybrid 100:10 0.2
net-mc clog 1

mc-spec clog repeat 10 sample-sigmas heatbath 0.95 hybrid 100:10 0.3 negate
net-mc clog 200
